Product Description

Bookshelves "U" - Set of 6 White Wall Shelves - STEEL - Made In Italy

  • Keep Your Books Suspended in Air !  As soon as you arrange your books, CDs or DVDs on them, the bookcase creates a magical illusion which will almost make it disappear in the background. Don’t you think this would make a stylish bookcase for your library?
  • Best QUALITY Shelves You Will Ever Find - Tired of those made in China cheap furniture that don’t last a year ? These shelves are extra thin and light and have been made of 2 millimeter thick steel in Italy. It will never bend ! Each shelf can hold up to 44 pounds !
  • Easy to Install: The durable floating shelves only need two screw to be fixed, just decide on which wall space is available for decorating and mount it with the hardware included in the packaging !
  • Each shelf can hold up to 44 pounds ! The top quality steel and the design of the shelves allow you to put everything you want on it, It will never bend!
  • Space Saver: The U-shaped shelves are perfect for Books, home accessories and decorative items. Create more floor space and move around freely in your small living room, the shelves offer 141,72 of usable length !

Pure functionality and functional purity

Contemporary Design: This is the best quality and designed floating shelf you will ever find.

Designed By Mauro Canfori, one of the masters in modern minimalistic design, the TEEbooks shelves are simple, light and functional. The sleek modern design U-shaped shelves offers a lot more than just organizing.

Each Shelf's Dimensions: 17 x 6 x 3.5 Inches 6 inch deep, 6 inch high, 23,5 inch long, weight 7 pounds.

Can be used for CDs, DVDs and Books !

Create an illusion of your favorite books, CDs or DVDs being suspended in mid air with this Wall Shelves.

This is a modular wall bookcase system which consists of 6 wall shelves. As soon as you arrange your books, CDs or DVDs on them, the bookcase creates a magical illusion which will almost make it disappear in the background.

What you get to see are your books or CDs suspended in mid air !

Each shelf can hold up to 44 pounds ! The top quality steel and the design of the shelves allow you to put everything you want on it, It will never bend !

  • Material: 2 millimeter thick steel
  • Color: White
  • Each Shelf's Dimensions:  6 inch deep, 6 inch high, 23,5 inch long,
  • Weight 7 pounds.

What is in the Package: Set of 6 23,5" long Metal White U-Shaped Bookshelves and Mounting Hardware

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzes reviews to verify trustworthiness.

4.0 out of 5 stars Minor cosmetic issues don't stop these shelves from looking great.
Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2017
Color: WhiteVerified Purchase
I love the way these look on our wall. We hired someone to put them up since I don't know how to use a level or a tape measure or a stud finder, but installation seemed easy enough.

The only reason I'm not giving these the full five stars is because about half of the ten shelves had some sort of cosmetic issue—scratches, smudges, weird globs of paint. The defects are small, though, so you don't see them unless you're really looking.

These are well made shelves. It is easy to install. It has some weight to it. Our DVDs and Blu-Rays fit nicely into them. The reason we bought these is we couldn't find any other floating shelves that fit DVDs, with sides on each side, except this. The shelves were shipped to our home very fast. Most of our DVDs fit on the shelf, but we may have to buy more to fit all of them on them, which is the only downside to these.

Michael Madden
1.0 out of 5 stars TERRIBLE PRODUCT
Reviewed in the United States on December 11, 2019
Color: White
THIS PRODUCT IS TERRIBLE! If I could give a negative star, I would. These shelves “flex” down and bow out from the wall - causing the books to tilt forward and splay out. I weighed the books that I placed on the shelf (well under 25 lbs and these shelves are rated for 40+ lbs), so I knew that wasn’t the issue. I also used shallow books (6” wide or less), but the shelf still flexed and my books tilted forward. I raised this issue with the manufacturer and was told that the shelves have a natural “elasticity” so the tilt is to be expected. NO WHERE IN THEIR PRODUCT DESCRIPTION DO THEY MENTION THAT THE SHELVES WILL FLEX OR TILT! I would not have purchased these shelves if I knew this would happen.

I purchased this product directly from Teebooks so I know they’re not a knock off. I request a return for refund which they won’t offer. TERRIBLE BUSINESS, TERRIBLE SERVICE, and TOTAL WASTE OF MONEY.
